  <brief_title>Efficacy of Pre-exposure Treatment With Hydroxy-Chloroquine on the Risk and Severity of COVID-19 Infection</brief_title>
  <acronym>PREPCOV</acronym>
  <official_title>Real-life Evaluation of the Efficacy of Pre-exposure Treatment With Hydroxy-Chloroquine on the Risk and Severity of COVID-19 Infection in Patients Receiving Long-term Treatment for Systemic Lupus Erythematosus and/or Gougerot's Disease</official_title>
